Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.06,0:08:13.20,对话-CN,,0,0,0,,是个女生\N{\fs45\b1\fnKozuka Gothic Pro B}女の子だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:17.98,对话-CN,,0,0,0,,人偶？\N{\fs45\b1\fnKozuka Gothic Pro B}人形
